  <div class="timeline-item">
    <div class="timeline-dot">M1</div>
    <div class="timeline-content">
      <h4>Month 1 — Basic Rankings</h4>
      <p>Blog posts aur website index ho jaati hai — branded searches pe aane lagte hain!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="timeline-item">
    <div class="timeline-dot">M3</div>
    <div class="timeline-content">
      <h4>Month 3 — Local Rankings</h4>
      <p>"Coaching bharatpur", "web designer bharatpur" jaise keywords pe ranking shuru!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="timeline-item">
    <div class="timeline-dot">M6</div>
    <div class="timeline-content">
      <h4>Month 6 — Strong Presence</h4>
      <p>Multiple keywords pe rank, regular traffic, leads aane lagte hain!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

