<h2>Aksar Puche Jaane Wale Sawaal</h2>

<h3>Q: Google Business Profile banane mein kitna paisa lagta hai?</h3>
<p>Bilkul FREE hai! Google Business Profile create karna, verify karna, aur manage karna — sab free hai. Koi hidden charges nahi!</p>

<h3>Q: Kitne time mein Google Maps pe dikh­ne lagenge?</h3>
<p>Verification ke baad 24-48 ghante mein Google Maps pe dikh­na shuru ho jaata hai. Search results mein aane mein 1-2 hafte lag sakte hain!</p>

<h3>Q: Kya bina address ke Google Business Profile ban sakti hai?</h3>
<p>Haan! Agar aap service-based business hain — jaise web designer, consultant — toh "Service area business" select kar sakte hain aur physical address hide kar sakte hain. Sirf service areas mention kar sakte hain!</p>

<h3>Q: Negative reviews kaise handle karein?</h3>
<p>Negative review ka professionally reply karo — "Hum aapki baat sunna chahte hain, please humse +91 XXXXX pe contact karein." Kabhi argue mat karo — Google aur customers dono dekhte hain!</p>

